                text = "*(A fence with a clerk's spectacles and a killer's calm, in the back of a pawnshop that smells of candle-tallow and other people's heirlooms.)* The dead thing. In my shop. *(He does not reach for a weapon, which is its own kind of threat.)* Word is you've got Roen Alleywind running at your heel, which means either you're someone the Guild should know, or you're someone the Guild should *remove* before the Harpers pay us to. I prefer knowing to removing. It's better for repeat business. Talk.",
