            {
                id = "1", speaker = "Quill-and-Ledger Mas",
                text = "Here's the Guild's arithmetic, and unlike the Doomguides', mine balances. The Harpers want you handled. The Choir wants you crowned. The church wants you caged. *(He polishes the spectacles.)* And the Guild wants whatever the others want, because that's the thing we can charge them all for. So tell me, walking miracle — are you a problem I sell, or a partner I protect? The price is the same to me. The difference is entirely up to you.",
